  "description": "A loyal squire for your next Minecraft adventure",
  "body": "<h2 style=\"text-align: center; color: #169179;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/animights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/animights?logo=modrinth&amp;labelColor=black&amp;color=1bd96a\" alt=\"Modrinth Downloads\" width=\"212\" height=\"29\"></a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/animights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1414819?logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=eb622b&amp;labelColor=black&amp;color=eb622b\" alt=\"CurseForge Downloads\" width=\"164\" height=\"28\"></a><a href=\"https://codderg.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Wiki-Read-2ea44f?logo=wikipedia&amp;logoColor=white&amp;style=flat&amp;labelColor=111\" alt=\"Wiki\" width=\"131\" height=\"30\"></a></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; color: #169179;\"><strong><img src=\"https://codderg.com/assets/images/animights/Logo.png\" alt=\"Animights\"></strong></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; color: #169179;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1441/495/2025-12-27_20-28-11-webp.webp\" alt=\"2025-12-27_20.28.11.webp\"></strong></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; color: #169179;\"><strong><br>REQUIRED TO RUN:</strong></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #169179;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/geckolib\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1081/393/64/64/638621132937140582.png\" alt=\"GeckoLib logo\"></a> <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/knight-lib\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img style=\"color: #fff;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1084/451/64/64/638625514374500036.png\" alt=\"Knight Lib logo\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></span></strong></h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h2>\n<p>Credits:</p>\n<p>My mom who gifted me Canito when I was a kid, a dog doll that inspired this mod.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Awesome artist <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/themodderg/projects\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">@ModderG</a> for helping make my childhood friend alive</p>\n<p>Big thanks to an anonymous hero who coded the project but wanted to keep his good-doing in secret (Starts with X and rhymes with \"Ilonity\").</p>\n<p>Future plans:</p>\n<p>We may or may not add other dog and cat variants as maybe other vanilla squieres (like axolotls or parrots, who knows?) but it will heavily depend on how this mod goes, it was made for me to play lol but it became a project I'm proud of.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_a7fc9f18-e19f-4887-b333-b9d2b42b6397.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"249\" height=\"260\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_6312cfce-8252-4d00-ab88-3f1c8e07802f.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"315\" height=\"258\"></p>",
